title: Justin Rowsell
text: Justin Rowsell (born 22 December 1971) is an Australian <a href="boxing">boxer</a>. He competed in the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%201992%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Lightweight">men's lightweight</a> event at the <a href="1992%20Summer%20Olympics">1992 Summer Olympics</a>.
